01:14:38.800 --> 01:14:40.660
growth hormone being one of them,

01:14:40.660 --> 01:14:44.580
there was well over a 50% five zero drop

01:14:44.580 --> 01:14:46.630
in their growth hormone release

01:14:46.630 --> 01:14:49.720
during alcohol laced sleep at night.

01:14:49.720 --> 01:14:53.050
- And growth hormone is
so vital for metabolism

01:14:53.050 --> 01:14:54.215
and repair of tissues.

01:14:54.215 --> 01:14:55.830
- Yeah, it's not just for kids.

01:14:55.830 --> 01:14:57.278
- [Andrew] Keeping body fat low.

01:14:57.278 --> 01:14:58.610
